## link::Classes/Osc::
|| arguments: code:: buffer number, frequency, phase, mul, add ::

code::
{ Osc.ar(80, 100, 0, 0.1) }.scope(1, zoom:4);

b.sine1(1.0/(1..12));
b.sine1(1.0/(1..24));
